<p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 15.75pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32.8pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">为进一步建设良好的校园艺术氛围，培养学生健康的审美情趣和良好的艺术修养，江西省开展了第十一届大学生艺术展活动。我校师生参与的作品在众多作品中脱颖而出，共获奖</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">3项。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 15.75pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32.8pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 15.75pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32.8pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-18%2010%3A21%3A15%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%201.png?Expires=2020904476&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=p5CfvnKVKDrlgCiGLnD3Riym7H0%3D" alt="" width="650" height="459" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 15.75pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32.8pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-18%2010%3A21%3A31%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%202.png?Expires=2020904491&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=ri8lrM6tJDv%2Fnk5spLxIkWgJ6pU%3D" alt="" width="650" height="426" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 15.75pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32.8pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 15.75pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32.8pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 15.75pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32.8pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">由饶子欢老师指导的戏剧类集体项目</span></span><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">《对不起我还是害怕》《只此一个月亮同学》</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">荣获</span></span><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">三等奖</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">；程慧敏老师指导的郭继臻同学的书法、篆刻作品类</span></span><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">《星火之势》</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">荣获</span></span><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">三等奖</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32.8pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">江西省大学生艺术展演活动每</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">3年举办一次，是江西省规格最高、规模最大、影响最广的大学生艺术盛会。此次活动充分展现出了我校的专业实力水平，对我校的专业建设有积极影响、起到了推动作用。今后我校将以此次展演为契机，坚持以美育人，继续带领江软师生参加各类艺术展演、比赛活动，继续营造良好的校园艺术文化氛围，不断完善学生美育实践平台，引领学生树立正确的审美观念、陶冶高尚的道德情操、塑造美好心灵，弘扬中华优秀传统文化，努力提升我校师生的专业水平与艺术素养，为我校美育建设作出更大贡献，为着力培养德智体美劳全面发展的社会主义建设者和接班人贡献力量。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>